# Namefi Astra Availability API - HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@authToken = {{AVAILABILITY_API_AUTH_KEY}}
@domain = available.today

### GET single domain availability (with Authorization for higher rate limits)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/availability?domain={{domain}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### GET single domain availability (no Authorization; lower rate limits)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/availability?domain={{domain}}
Accept: application/json

### POST bulk domain availability
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/availability/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "domains": [
    "available.today",
    "ends.today",
    "promos.today"
  ]
}
